Package com.ziluck.factions.events

Events fired by the Factions plugin.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CancellableFactionEvent
    A FactionEvent that is able to be cancelled.
    FactionCreateEvent
    When a Faction is created for the first time.
    FactionEvent
    An event related to Factions.
    FactionLookupEvent
    Fired when a player tries to look up a Faction by it's name.
    FactionUnusedNameCheckEvent
    The event that is fired when a player attempts to create a new Faction, and the server checks if the name is used.
